Palo Alto Networks Inc And Vmware Inc Transform Cloud Deployments With Integrated Network Virtualization And Security Solution
Tuesday, 19 Nov 2013 08:00am EST
Palo Alto Networks Inc and VMware, Inc. announced a partnership backed by a new jointly-developed solution. The integrated solution will enable customers to use the VMware NSX network virtualization platform to automate provisioning and distribution of Palo Alto Networks network security in their software-defined data centers. Recognizing these changing requirements, Palo Alto Networks and VMware have partnered to deliver an integrated solution that combines the Palo Alto Networks VM-Series virtualized security platform with the VMware NSX network virtualization platform. With this joint solution, customers will be able to unify network security across their physical and virtual environments with a single point of management.Â 
